	<tr>
		
			<td colspan="2" bgcolor="#DEDACB" background="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/tb_beige.gif">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				Info on this song. 11-06-00<BR>
<BR>
Starts off low, every 6 levels it increases by 2 hp with instrument, 1 without. Gypsy Lute only increases effectiveness by 5% and costs about 300pp. Only useful at high levels really.<BR>
<BR>
So here's how it goes. (Sitting w/lute)<BR>
Level 6 - 6hp<BR>
Level 12 - 8hp<BR>
Level 18 - 10hp<BR>
Level 20 (you gain 1 hp per tick sitting due to level 20 cap. So 11hp from here now)<BR>
Level 24 - 13hp<BR>
Level 30 - 15hp<BR>
Level 36 - 17hp<BR>
Level 42 - 19hp<BR>
Level 48 - 21hp<BR>
<BR>
Remember that certain instruments can affect the effectiveness of this song. At level 48 w/Gypsy Lute you gotta add 5% to the 21hp and that's the effectiveness on healing.<BR>
<BR>
Passionate Memories<BR>
30 bard
				</font>
			</td>

	</tr>
	
